      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It sounds like you're going through a very heavy and difficult time, and I'm so sorry you're feeling this way. Please know that these feelings of emptiness are real, but they don't have to be permanent. If you're feeling overwhelmed or hopeless, reaching out to a trusted friend, family member, or mental health professional can provide support and help you find a path forward. You are not alone in this struggle, and there are people who care about you and want to help.",
